quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  12,30,Some zensky mesto gossiped governor's manzelka bol trying zvadzat ju servant! Ona bol deeply do laska him! My see ona ist astray
  12,31,When ona heard ich gossip ona invited them chystat them comfortable miesto dat each z them noz! Ona potom said do him Zapisat ich izba When they saw him they admired him ze they rez ich hands They said Glory je do GOD this nie bol human bol this bol honorable angel
  12,32,Ona said This bol 1 ona blamed mna falling v laska s! Ja robi indeed try zvadzat him he refused he robi co ja command him robi he iste ist zalar debased
  12,33,He said Moj Lord zalar je lepsie than dat them. Ona divert ich kut plany mna ja desire them behave mat rad ignorant jeden
  12,34,Jeho Lord answered jeho prayer diverted ich kut plany z him. He bol Hearer Omniscient
  12,35,Noskorsie they saw it zretelny proofs lenze they imprison him for awhile